    <h2>âš¡ How It Works</h2>
    <ol>
        <li>ğŸ” The firewall agent <strong>monitors active network connections</strong>.</li>
        <li>ğŸ“¡ It <strong>fetches policies</strong> from the centralized server.</li>
        <li>ğŸš¨ If a connection matches <span class="highlight">blocked rules</span>, it is <strong>blocked</strong> via Windows Firewall.</li>
        <li>ğŸ“œ The decision (<span class="highlight">allow/block</span>) is <strong>logged</strong> in MongoDB.</li>
        <li>ğŸ¤– AI detects anomalies and <strong>blocks suspicious traffic</strong>.</li>
    </ol>

